	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I looked at the English translation (I'm assuming that's what you're working off from)<br /><br />The text coding is not compressed, it's just mixed up.<br /><br />I sent you a quick text file explaining the letter coding. I'm afraid there's not going to be an easy way to find all the text. Unless you can code a conversion tool converting all the hex values to the correct ascii value.<br /><br />It does seem that (at least from the first few seconds of the game) that text strings start with EB and end with FF. And starts somewhere around $30000 of the ROM. Hope this helps.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


